properties.Name: EquifaxAlert
properties.Description: Alerts: Provides alert notices to indicate key differences between the inquiry information and the file content; may also return alerts from a requested consumer product (e.g., FACT Act alerts or other event that may warrant additional attention).

Columns.Name: EfxId
Columns.Description: The EFX ID™ is a unique and persistent nine-digit number that identifies and tracks the business unit with which you have the credit relationship;

Columns.Name: ProfileTimestamp
Columns.Description:
Provides the timestamp when the inquiry was made as recorded
by Equifax (Eastern Time).

Columns.Name: AlertId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an alert.
